thread.title: Tammy Correia
thread.title_full: Mabel's Labels reviewed by Tammy Correia

author: Tammy Correia
title: Tammy Correia
text: I love the quality of Mabel's labels as well as the fast delivery and accuracy of the labels. Never had a problem and have used this company for many years. I've tried lesser cost brands but definitely not satisfied. No other company has labels made this well. Definitely worth the money.
